  "type": "consumable",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "folder": "fhSubModern00001",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>An oil-based stack of underground origin. Used responsibly it produces a measurable strength gain; used carelessly it produces a coroner's report. Discipline is the difference, and discipline is written down.</p><p><strong><em>Desired effects on use.</em></strong> For 10 minutes you gain a +2 bonus to Strength (Athletics) checks, a +1 bonus to Strength-based weapon attack rolls, and your walking speed increases by 5 feet.</p><p><strong><em>On use, save against addiction.</em></strong> Make a DC 15 Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, you gain the Addicted condition from Black Lift (see below).</p><p><strong><em>Addicted from Black Lift.</em></strong> While you have this Addicted condition, you are also Poisoned, have disadvantage on Constitution saving throws, and your walking speed is reduced by 5 feet.</p><p><strong><em>Withdrawal Modifier: 6.</em></strong> Withdrawal lasts max(6 − your Constitution modifier, 3) long rests, minimum 1.</p><p><em>Requires: Tincture Dropper AND Athlete's Logbook.</em></p>"
    },
